Reproduction of benchmark test case E formulated in AIJ guidelines for
practical applications of CFD to pedestrian wind environment around
buildings

Creator: Masashi IMANO <masashi.imano@gmail.com>
Date: 25/Dec/2011
Supported OpenFOAM version: 2.0, 2.1

